  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "8e1b5141-0751-4599-b361-4d9b51ccef82",
    "name": "InventoryManagementAPI",
    "description": "## Inventory management API\n\nREST API for managing products, providers, and categories. Built with Bun, Elysia, Drizzle ORM, and PostgreSQL.\n\n## Base URL\n\nSet the `base_url` collection variable to your API root:\n\n- Local: `http://localhost:3000/api/v1`\n    \n\n## Authentication\n\nNo authentication required.\n\n## Resources\n\n**Products** — CRUD operations for products. Supports provider associations via `providerIds` and category assignment via `categoryId`.\n\n**Providers** — CRUD operations for providers (suppliers).\n\n**Categories** — CRUD operations for product categories.\n\n## Query Features (GET list endpoints)\n\nAll list endpoints (`GET /products`, `GET /providers`, `GET /categories`) support:\n\n- **Pagination**: `?page=1&limit=20`\n    \n- **Field selection**: `?fields=id,name,price`\n    \n- **Sorting**: `?sort=name` (asc) or `?sort=-price` (desc). Comma-separated for multiple: `?sort=name,-price`\n    \n- **Filtering**: exact match `?name=laptop`, partial match `?name[like]=lap`, range `?price[gte]=100&price[lte]=500`, boolean `?isActive=true`\n    \n\n## Response Format\n\nAll responses follow a consistent envelope:\n\n**Success (single resource):**\n\n``` json\n{ \"success\": true, \"data\": { ... } }\n\n ```\n\n**Success (list):**\n\n``` json\n{ \"success\": true, \"data\": [...], \"meta\": { \"page\": 1, \"limit\": 10, \"offset\": 0, \"totalItems\": 50, \"totalPages\": 5 } }\n\n ```\n\n**Error:**\n\n``` json\n{ \"success\": false, \"error\": { \"code\": \"NOT_FOUND\", \"message\": \"Product not found\" } }\n\n ```\n\n## Status Codes\n\n- `200` — Successful GET, PATCH\n    \n- `201` — Successful POST\n    \n- `204` — Successful DELETE\n    \n- `400` — Bad request / invalid input\n    \n- `404` — Resource not found\n    \n- `422` — Validation error\n    \n- `500` — Internal server error\n    \n\n---",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "18898473",
    "_collection_link": "https://go.postman.co/collection/18898473-8e1b5141-0751-4599-b361-4d9b51ccef82?source=collection_link"
